影片改编自威尔2011年[[火星任務_(小說)|同名小说]]，由斯科特执导，[[德魯·戈達德|德魯·戈達德]]编剧。[[二十世紀福斯|二十世紀福斯]]在2013年3月{{tsl|en|option (filmmaking)|改编权购买|买下}}小说改编权，制片人[[賽門·金柏格|賽門·金柏格]]负责将小说开发成电影<ref>{{cite journal | last=Kroll | first=Justin | url=https://variety.com/2013/film/news/fox-finds-martian-for-simon-kinberg-exclusive-1200007238/ | title=Fox Finds ‘Martian’ For Simon Kinberg | journal=Variety | date=March 12, 2013 | accessdate=August 25, 2015 }}</ref>。5月份，金柏格和片方就影片的编剧和导演展开谈判<ref>{{cite news | last=Sneider | first=Jeff | url=http://www.thewrap.com/drew-goddard-negotiations-write-direct-martian-fox-exclusive-91896/ | title=Drew Goddard in Negotiations to Write and Direct 'The Martian' for Fox | work=TheWrap | date=May 15, 2013 | accessdate=August 25, 2015 }}</ref>。金柏格写剧本，[[马特·戴蒙|马特·戴蒙]]表示金柏格执导的话，有兴趣参演。戈達德后来找机会导演漫画改编电影《[[邪惡六人組|邪惡六人組]]》<ref>{{cite news | last=Tilly | first=Chris | url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/06/17/matt-damon-explains-why-the-martian-is-a-love-letter-to-science | title=Matt Damon Explains Why The Martian is a Love Letter to Science | publisher=IGN | date=June 17, 2015 | accessdate=August 26, 2015 }}</ref>。金柏格之后买下《火星救援》原著，吸引斯科特的注意<ref>{{cite journal | last=Kroll | first=Justin | url=https://variety.com/2014/film/news/michael-pena-the-martian-matt-damon-ridley-scott-1201307660/ | title=Michael Pena Circles Ridley Scott's 'The Martian' With Matt Damon | journal=Variety | date=September 24, 2014 | accessdate=August 26, 2015 }}</ref>。2014年5月，斯科特和片方就达蒙饰演片中滞留宇航员一角洽谈<ref>{{cite journal | last=Kroll | first=Justin | url=https://variety.com/2014/film/news/ridley-scott-in-talks-to-direct-foxs-the-martian-with-matt-damon-1201180062/ | title=Ridley Scott in Talks to Direct Fox’s 'The Martian' With Matt Damon | journal=Variety | date=May 13, 2014 | accessdate=August 25, 2015 }}</ref>。斯科特说，他被科学的强调吸引住，认为可能实现寓教于乐的平衡。达蒙也说他被小说、剧本和与斯科特合作的机会迷上了<ref>{{cite news | last=White | first=James | url=http://www.empireonline.com/features/the-martian-at-NASA | title=Inside The Martian: Empire Meets NASA | work=[[帝國雜誌|Empire]] | date=August 2015 | accessdate=September 1, 2015 }}</ref>。斯科特确认参与后，计划迅速获得批准，步入正轨<ref>{{cite journal | last=Kroll | first=Justin | url=https://variety.com/2014/film/news/jessica-chastain-to-joins-matt-damon-in-ridley-scotts-the-martian-1201214554/ | title=Jessica Chastain Joins Matt Damon in Ridley Scott's 'The Martian' | journal=Variety | date=September 3, 2014 | accessdate=August 26, 2015 }}</ref>。戈達德后来告诉《剧本创意》（{{lang|en|''Creative Screenwriting''}}）杂志表示，和他相比，斯科特拍这部电影要好得多：“既然是斯科特，协调就不在话下，因为我很尊敬他。每天我都会环顾四周，想着‘雷德利·斯科特真的在做这部作品吗？太让人兴奋了<ref>{{cite web|url=http://creativescreenwriting.com/life-goes-on-drew-goddard-on-the-martian/|title=Life Goes On: Drew Goddard on The Martian|last=McKittrick|first=Christopher|date=August 20, 2015|publisher=Creative Screenwriting|accessdate=August 20, 2015}}</ref>！’”

=== 摄制 ===
[[File:Mountain_in_Wadi_Rum,_Jordan.jpg|thumbnail]][[瓦地伦|瓦地伦]]。]]

影片内景于匈牙利首府[[布达佩斯|布达佩斯]]以西26公里的制酒重镇[[艾杰克|艾杰克]]的{{le|科罗达制片厂|Korda Studios}}搭建。里面拥有世界最大的[[片场系统|片场系统]]<ref>{{cite news | last=Daniels | first=Nia | url=http://www.kftv.com/news/2014/09/18/ridley-scotts-the-martian-sets-up-to-film-in-hungary | title=Ridley Scott’s The Martian sets up to film in Hungary | publisher=KFTV | date=September 18, 2014 | accessdate=August 26, 2015 }}</ref><ref name="weintraub">{{cite news | last=Weintraub | first=Steve | url=http://collider.com/the-martian-set-visit-30-things-to-know/ | title=Over 30 Things to Know About Ridley Scott's ''The Martian'' from our Budapest Set Visit | publisher=Collider.com | date=June 17, 2015 | accessdate=August 26, 2015 }}</ref>。影片于2014年11月24日开拍<ref>{{cite journal | last=Foundas | first=Scott | url=https://variety.com/2014/film/news/ridley-scott-exodus-gods-and-kings-christian-bale-1201363668/ | title='Exodus: Gods and Kings' Director Ridley Scott on Creating His Vision of Moses | journal=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] | date=November 25, 2014 | accessdate=August 26, 2015 }}</ref>。斯科特选择用3D摄影机拍摄影片<ref name="haricharan" />。大约20套布景为影片搭建（斯科特2014年作品《[[法老与众神|法老与众神]]》有70套布景，2007年作品《[[美國黑幫_(電影)|美國黑幫]]》有100多套）。取景片场旁边的片场中种植着货真价实的马铃薯<ref name="klimek">{{cite journal | last=Klimek | first=Chris | url=http://www.airspacemag.com/daily-planet/matt-damon-first-farmer-mars-180956410/ | title=Matt Damon, First Farmer on Mars | journal=Air & Space/Smithsonian | date=August 28, 2015 | accessdate=September 1, 2015 }}</ref>。六人团队为影片设计了15套服装。马特·达蒙在场的部分外景于2015年3月在[[联合国教育、科学及文化组织|联合国教科文组织]]世界遗产地[[约旦|约旦]][[瓦地伦|瓦地伦]]取景，一共拍了八天<ref name="weintraub" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.jordantimes.com/news/local/ridley-scott-hany-abu-asad-shoot-their-latest-movies-jordan|title=Ridley Scott, Hany Abu Asad shoot their latest movies in Jordan|date=March 16, 2015|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sponsored/travel/jordan-places-to-visit/11888487/wadi-rum-desert-tours.html|title=Wadi Rum: a mesmerising desert guarded by stone giants|accessdate=October 8, 2015|date=October 1, 2015|work=The Daily Telegraph}}</ref>。瓦地伦也是其他火星背景电影的取景地，例如2000年的《[[火星任務_(2000年電影)|火星任务]]》和《[[红色星球|红色星球]]》、2013年的《{{tsl|en|The Last Days on Mars|火星上的最后时日}}》<ref>{{cite news | author=Staff | url=http://www.albawaba.com/entertainment/that's-a-wrap!-hollywood's-%22the-martian%22-and-palestine's-%22arab-idol%22-in-jordan-670308 | title=That's a wrap! Hollywood's 'The Martian' and Palestine's 'Arab Idol' finish scenes in Jordan | work=The Jordan Times | date=March 17, 2015 | accessdate=August 26, 2015 }}</ref>。影片的拍摄总共持续了大约70天<ref name="weintraub" />。一架特制火星车模型为影片搭建，为了对約旦人民的热情好客表示感谢，主创团队向他们赠送了这架模型，模型目前在约旦{{tsl|en|Royal Automobile Museum|皇家汽车博物馆}}展览<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ameinfo.com/media-and-marketing/media/cinema/the-royal-automobile-museum-patrons-the-premiere-of-the-martian-film/#sthash.eoBeIKI4.dpuf|accessdate=October 22, 2015|date=October 22, 2015|title=The Royal Automobile Museum patrons the premiere of 'The Martian' film|work=ameinfo|publisher=Mediaquest Corp.}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2015/10/02/entertainment/the-martian-review-thr/|title=Review: 'The Martian' is a pleasure|accessdate=October 8, 2015|date=October 5, 2015|publisher= CNN}}</ref>。

威尔在他的小说中避免写道惠特尼孤独绝望。惠特尼的幽默特质在影片中保留，斯科特还展现了主角在荒芜、尘埃滚滚的火星景观中孤独。《[[荷里活報道|荷里活報道]]》的{{tsl|en|Todd McCarthy|托德·麦卡锡}}写道：“回到地球上的场景为火星的干旱带来忙碌、数量稠密的配重，得到约旦瓦地伦附近地区的外景的辉煌呈现<ref>{{cite news|last1=McCarthy|first1=Todd|title='The Martian': TIFF Review|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/martian-tiff-review-820882|accessdate=May 30, 2016|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=September 11, 2015}}</ref>。”达蒙表示，他和斯科特受到展现受困登山者的2003年纪录电影《{{tsl|en|Touching the Void (film)|冰峰168小时}}》启发<ref name="hutchinson">{{cite news | last=Hutchinson | first=Lee | url=https://arstechnica.com/the-multiverse/2015/08/ars-talks-with-matt-damon-on-being-astronaut-mark-watney-in-the-martian/ | title=Ars talks with Matt Damon on being astronaut Mark Watney in ''The Martian'' |website=Ars Technica | date=August 27, 2015 | accessdate=September 1, 2015 }}</ref>。斯科特还希望片中惠特尼像[[鲁滨逊漂流记|鲁滨逊]]这个与世隔绝的角色，但认为片中他又有点不同，因为他在各种任务摄影机的监控下自行监测他的行为<ref name="klimek" />。

按照斯科特的说法，影片剪辑第一版长达2小时45分钟<ref>{{cite news|title=Ridley Scott Talks ‘The Martian’ Extended Cut and More|url=http://collider.com/ridley-scott-talks-the-martian-extended-cut-deleted-scenes-and-more/|accessdate=June 28, 2016|date=September 28, 2015}}</ref>。家用媒体发行的是加长版<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.movie-censorship.com/news.php?ID=9539 |title=The Martian – Ridley Scott Confirms Extended Cut |date=September 23, 2015 |first=Gerald |last=Wurm |publisher=Movie-Censorship.com |accessdate=January 5, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=The Martian Extended Cut Has 10 Minutes of New Footage|url=http://collider.com/the-martian-extended-edition-details/|accessdate=May 28, 2016|work=Collider|date=April 30, 2016}}</ref>。

=== NASA的参与 ===
[[File:NASA_Journey_to_Mars_and_“The_Martian"_(201508180009HQ).jpg|thumbnail]]留下手印，吉姆·埃里克森（左）和{{tsl|en|Andrew J. Feustel|安德鲁·J·费斯特尔}}（右）陪同在侧。]]

小说发行时，[[美国国家航空航天局|美国国家航空航天局]]邀请威尔参观[[林顿·约翰逊太空中心|林顿·约翰逊太空中心]]和[[喷气推进实验室|喷气推进实验室]]。斯科特开始准备影片时，威尔联系航空航天局协拍<ref name="bradley">{{cite news | last=Bradley | first=Ryan | url=http://www.popsci.com/why-nasa-helped-ridley-scott-create-martian-film-and-what-means-future-sci-fi-space-movies | title=Why NASA Helped Ridley Scott Create 'The Martian' Film | work=Popular Science | date=August 19, 2015 | accessdate=August 28, 2015 }}</ref>。斯科特和制片人{{tsl|en|Mark Huffam|马克·赫芬姆}}举行第一次制作会议时，他们打电话给航空航天局，和局子的电影和电视联络员伯特·乌尔里奇（{{lang|de|Bert Ulrich}}）对话<ref name="lidz">{{cite journal | last=Lidz | first=Gogo | url=http://www.newsweek.com/2015/10/02/why-nasa-faked-mars-landing-374214.html | title=NASA and 'The Martian': It Was Written in the Stars | work=Newsweek | date=September 20, 2015 | accessdate=October 2, 2015 }}</ref>。航空航天局看到影片有推广太空探索的潜质，决定协助剧组刻画片中的科学和技术<ref name="bradley" />。参与合作的航空航天局重要职员有行星科学处处长{{tsl|en|James L. Green|詹姆斯·L·格林}}和太阳系探索项目执行官{{tsl|en|Dave Lavery|戴夫·拉弗利}}<ref name="lidz" />。开拍前，斯科特和格林有过两次交谈。在一个月的时间内，航空航天局每周回答问题，总共数百个，从放射性同位素系统，到日后火星宇航员住所“棚屋”的可能模样。这些问题由格林回答，或是交给相关的专家，之后转交给斯科特团队，让他们为制片找路子<ref name="latimes">{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-mn-the-martian-movie-mars-water-matt-damon-20150929-story.html|title=For Matt Damon movie 'The Martian,' lots of research – and a watery coincidence|first=Steven |last=Zeitchik|work=Los Angeles Times|date=September 29, 2015|accessdate=October 2, 2015}}</ref><ref name="wall">{{cite news | last=Wall | first=Mike | url=http://www.space.com/30327-the-martian-movie-nasa-photos.html | title='The Martian' Lands at NASA's Mars Mission Control (Photos) | publisher=Space.com | date=August 20, 2015 | accessdate=August 28, 2015 }}</ref>。航空航天局还发去数百张火星和展现计算机显示屏模样的控制中心的图像文件<ref name="nasa"/>。格林安排布景师{{tsl|en|Arthur Max|亚瑟·麦克斯}}参观[[休斯敦|休斯敦]]约翰逊太空中心，亚瑟花了八个钟头会见了多位专家，拿到数百张图片<ref name="latimes"/><ref name="nasa"/>。布景团队在片场搭建了非常现代化的未来主义任务控制中心。在《[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]》看来，这描绘了“我们所有人幻想的太空中心”，一反约翰逊中心“衰败大学校园”模样<ref name="The Martian brings science, largely unchanged, from book to screen">{{cite web|last1=Hutchinson|first1=Lee|title=The Martian brings science, largely unchanged, from book to screen|url=https://arstechnica.com/the-multiverse/2015/09/the-martian-brings-science-largely-unchanged-from-book-to-screen/|website=Ars Technica|accessdate=October 4, 2015}}</ref>。

《[[新闻周刊|新闻周刊]]》称，航空航天局在影片中的合作超出大多数电影：“航空航天局许多部门的员工都在影片中进行咨询，从剧本开发到主体摄影，再到现在帮助宣传到剧院上映”<ref name="lidz" />。期间，航空航天局的制片联络员将影片剧本首页于2014年12月5日搭载于执行{{tsl|en|Exploration Flight Test 1|探索飞行任务1号}}的[[猎户座飞船|猎户座飞船]]<ref>{{cite news | last=Vilkomerson | first=Sara | url=http://www.ew.com/article/2014/12/19/ridley-scott-martian-script-into-space | title=Ridley Scott sends his 'Martian' script into space | work=[[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] | date=December 19, 2014 | accessdate=September 1, 2015 }}</ref>。

《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》表示航空航天局和科学界普遍认为影片是普及[[載人火星任務|載人-{}-火星-{}-任務]]的办法。《纽约时报》报道称影片是“航空航天局的完美植入，他们在其网站上宣传这部影片已经得到回报。星期一（2015年9月28日），科学家宣布[[火星侦察轨道器|火星侦察轨道器]]摄影机拍到的画面出现了液态水的标志<ref name="NASA-20150928">{{cite web |last1=Webster |first1=Guy |last2=Agle |first2=DC |last3=Brown |first3=Dwayne |last4=Cantillo |first4=Laurie |title=NASA Confirms Evidence That Liquid Water Flows on Today's Mars |url=http://www.jpl.nasa.gov/news/news.php?feature=4722 |date=28 September 2015 |publisher=NASA |accessdate=28 September 2015 }}</ref><ref name="NYT-20150928">{{cite news |last=Chang |first=Kenneth |title=NASA Says Signs of Liquid Water Flowing on Mars |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/09/29/science/space/mars-life-liquid-water.html |date=28 September 2015 |work=The New York Times |accessdate=28 September 2015 }}</ref>，这时机暗示航空航天局一定拿下了整个跨界宣传活动<ref name="NYT-20151001" />。”航空航天局项目经理吉姆·埃里克森表示将向观众展示[[太空航行對人體的影響|人类前往火星的“风险和回报”]]<ref name="dave">{{cite news | last=Dave | first=Paresh | url=http://www.latimes.com/science/la-fi-martian-movie-science-20150820-story.html | title=Why NASA scientists are excited about Matt Damon film 'The Martian' | work=Los Angeles Times | date=August 19, 2015 | accessdate=September 1, 2015 }}</ref>。

2015年10月，航空航天局上线了追随惠特尼火星跋涉征程的网页工具<ref name="NASA-20151008b">{{cite web |last=Gipson |first=Lillian |title=Follow Mark Watney’s Epic Trek on Mars with New NASA Web Tool |url=http://www.nasa.gov/feature/follow-mark-watney-s-epic-trek-on-mars-with-new-nasa-web-tool |date=October 8, 2015 |publisher=[[美国国家航空航天局|NASA]] |accessdate=October 29, 2015 }}</ref>，并详述未来的计划和[[现实|现实]]中{{le|人类登陆火星任务|Human mission to Mars|人类旅行火星}}中[[太空航行對人體的影響|太空航行對人體的影響]]<ref name="AP-20151029">{{cite news |last=Dunn |first=Marcia |title=Report: NASA needs better handle on health hazards for Mars |url=http://apnews.excite.com/article/20151029/us-sci-space-travel-health-6dfd5b2c76.html |date=October 29, 2015 |work=AP News |accessdate=October 30, 2015 }}</ref><ref name="NASA-20151029oig">{{cite web |author=Staff |title=NASA's Efforts to Manage Health and Human Performance Risks for Space Exploration (IG-16-003) |url=https://oig.nasa.gov/audits/reports/FY16/IG-16-003.pdf |format=PDF |date=October 29, 2015 |work=NASA |accessdate=October 29, 2015 }}</ref><ref name="NASA-20151008">{{cite web |title= REPORT: NASA’s Pioneering Next Steps in Space Exploration |url= http://www.nasa.gov/sites/default/files/atoms/files/journey-to-mars-next-steps-20151008_508.pdf |format=PDF |date= October 8, 2015 |publisher=NASA |accessdate= October 29, 2015 }}</ref><ref name="CAP-20151028">{{cite web |author=Staff |title= Human Space Exploration: The Next Steps |url= https://www.americanprogress.org/events/2015/10/19/123515/human-space-exploration-the-next-steps/ |date=October 28, 2015 |publisher=Center for American Progress |accessdate=October 29, 2015 }}</ref><ref name="Video-20151028">{{cite web |author=Staff |title=NASA: "Human Space Exploration – The Next Steps" – Video (55:48) |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bem-Lqsg_9U |publisher=Center for American Progress |date=October 28, 2015 |accessdate=October 29, 2015 }}</ref>

